---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Closing Accounts collects no personal data. No analytics, no cookies, no tracking.">
<div class="page-hero">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
</div>
<section class="card">
  <p>Closing Accounts collects no personal data. We use no analytics. We set no cookies. We don't track your browsing. We don't know who you are.</p>
  <p>This site is static HTML served through Cloudflare Pages. No server-side code processes your requests. No database stores your visits.</p>
  <p>We recognize that people who use this site are often going through one of the most difficult periods of their lives. We have designed the site deliberately so that your use of it, including which pages you read, how long you spend, and what you're going through, is not recorded anywhere. You can read about any topic here, at any hour, without leaving a trace.</p>
  <p>If you email us, we receive your email. We don't add you to a list. We don't sell your address. We reply if a reply is needed and that's the end of it.</p>
  <p>This site exists to help people through a difficult process with clear information and honest guidance. We start by not making anything harder than it needs to be.</p>
  <p style="color: var(--text-light); font-size: 0.8rem;">Last updated: April 2026</p>
</section>
</Layout>
